{% extends "project/project-base.html.twig" %}

{% block title %}Rules{% endblock %}

{% block body %}
    <style>
        .title-bird {
            display: none;
        }
        .blackboard-container {
            display: none;
        }
        .blackboard-container.active {
            display: block;
        }
    </style>

    <h1 class="project-h1">Game Rules</h1>
    <br>

    <button class="blackjack-button navlink-project2" id="toggle-button" onclick="toggleBoards()">Show Poker Patience Rules</button>

    <div class="doc-container">
        <div class="blackjack-rules-project">
            <div class="blackboard-container active" id="blackjack-rules">
                <a href="{{ asset('img/blackboard-dark.svg') }}">
                    <img class="blackboard" src="{{ asset('img/blackboard5.svg') }}" alt="Blackboard SVG Dark Theme"/>
                </a>
                <div class="blackboard-rules">
                    <pre>
            <span class="blackboard-rubric">BLACKJACK-RULES</span>
            Both the dealer and player wager 100 chips each per hand - no exceptions
            Dealer must hit if hand is less than 17
            Dealer must stand if hand is greater than or equal to 17
            Dealer's and player's hands are evaluated equally
            Dealer's and player's hands interact equally with aces
            No bonuses for a clean Blackjack-hand (A♠<span class="red">K♥</span>) and the like:
            it's a beautiful hand, but it's treated and rewarded normally,
            for dealer and player alike
            200 for won hand, 100 for drawn, 0 for lost (slightly redundant)
            Game is concluded when the dealer or player has won all the chips
            Otherwise the normal <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Blackjack">Blackjack-rules</a> apply.
                    </pre>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="poker-patience-rules-project">
            <div class="blackboard-container" id="poker-patience-rules">
                <a href="{{ asset('img/blackboard-dark.svg') }}">
                    <img class="blackboard" src="{{ asset('img/blackboard5.svg') }}" alt="Blackboard SVG Dark Theme"/>
                </a>
                <div class="blackboard-rules">
                    <pre>
            <span class="blackboard-rubric">POKER PATIENCE-RULES</span>
            With 25 cards, 5x5, build 5 Poker hands horizontally, and 5 vertically,
            and try to maximize your score.

            Pair - 2p
            Two Pair - 5p
            Three Of A Kind - 10p
            Straight - 15p
            Flush - 20p
            Full House - 25p
            Four Of A Kind - 50p
            Straight Flush - 75p
            Royal Straight Flush - 150p
                    </pre>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <script>
        function toggleBoards() {
            const blackjackRules = document.getElementById('blackjack-rules');
            const pokerPatienceRules = document.getElementById('poker-patience-rules');
            const toggleButton = document.getElementById('toggle-button');

            if (blackjackRules.classList.contains('active')) {
                blackjackRules.classList.remove('active');
                pokerPatienceRules.classList.add('active');
                toggleButton.textContent = 'Show Blackjack Rules';
            } else {
                blackjackRules.classList.add('active');
                pokerPatienceRules.classList.remove('active');
                toggleButton.textContent = 'Show Poker Patience Rules';
            }
        }
    </script>
{% endblock %}
